    "image_with_text_t6KzFw": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CcwiLn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/idlehourscafe_/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Idle Hours Cafe</span></a> invites you to slow down, sip thoughtfully, and savor the moment in a world that moves at a mile-a-minute. What started as a cozy at-home experiment with friends has blossomed into a pop-up café experience specializing in matcha, coffee, and seasonal drinks designed to delight.</p><p>Meet Aanchal and Aditi, the creators behind Idle Hours, and our partners for our upcoming <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/pages/holiday-2025-sip-and-shops\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.getplenty.com/pages/holiday-2025-sip-and-shops\">Holiday Sip & Shop</a>, happening at select locations December 7-11. Find event details and RSVPs <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/pages/holiday-2025-sip-and-shops\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.getplenty.com/pages/holiday-2025-sip-and-shops\">here</a>.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_CcwiLn"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_3414.heic",
        "height": "adapt",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "image_first",
        "desktop_content_position": "middle",
        "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
        "content_layout": "no-overlap",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "mobile_content_alignment": "left",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_wKVLmh": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CLbqn8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q:</strong> What inspired you to start Idle Hours?</p><p><strong>A: </strong>We have always loved hosting in our space, from holiday dinners to wine nights, charcuterie boards and movie nights; we had done it all… except a cafe. Idle Hours began as a simple way to bring our friends together in our apartment, unwind, and experiment with unique drinks. We quickly realized that we really wanted to share this with more people, and we just hit the ground running with our little idea.</p><p><strong>Q:</strong> Idle Hours is all about slowing down. What does a “perfect idle hour” look like to you?</p><p><strong>A:</strong> For us, the “perfect idle hour” is all about finding some time for the little joys of life, whether that be indulging in our morning matcha or taking the time to do our skincare routine. It really doesn’t have to be anything big or monumental, just a small pocket of time that makes us feel grounded and present.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_CLbqn8"
      ],
